Texts.Chs: '我们听到那些不会被淹没的声音.'这就是声音之海: 我们离碎心国很近了,在那里没有什么是真正死亡的.
Texts.Eng: 'We hear those voices that will not be drowned.' This is the Sea of Voices: we are close to Polythreme, where nothing is truly dead.

Texts.Chs: 一座占位的城市,其高耸的特征在你面前模糊褪色, 一处奇迹的瞬间所在。
Texts.Eng: A Placeholder city, its towering features squint and fade before you, a wonder of momentary existance.

Texts.Chs: 起了一阵似乎被烘烤过的微风, 虽然你知道这不可能,但是风里确实有远方沙漠的气味.你现在离盐狮很近了.
Texts.Eng: A baked breeze rises, the improbable scent of stone out of some distant desert. You are close to the Salt Lions.

Texts.Chs: 一朵淡黄色的光组成的花朵出现在了南方的地平线上! 你靠近了瓦尔查斯, 镜之城.
Texts.Eng: A buttery bloom of light on the southern horizon! You approach Varchas, the Mirrored City.

Texts.Chs: 深红色的浪花泛起.我们正在接近亚当之路, 那里流着光明之山的血.'.
Texts.Eng: A carmine tint to the waves. We're approaching Adam's Way, 'where flows the Mountain's blood'.

Texts.Chs: 一根无形的丝线拂过你的脸.空气正在提示蜘蛛你来了.
Texts.Eng: A floating strand of web caresses your face. The air hints at spiders.

Texts.Chs: 一座宏伟的房子矗立在一个不起眼的小岛上
Texts.Eng: A grand house rises over a humble isle

Texts.Chs: 一阵突如其来的孢子雾气! 水手们打着喷嚏. 声音在粘稠的空气中回荡.
Texts.Eng: A sudden fog of spores! Zailors sneeze. The sound echoes flatly in the soupy air.

Texts.Chs: 现在我们进入了卡勒穆尼. 空气中是狂野和荣耀的气息.某种光.为什么水手们会害怕这地方?
Texts.Eng: And now we enter the Calumnies. There is a wild and glorious scent in the air. A kind of light. Why do zailors fear this place?

Texts.Chs: 海面上漂着另一只海兽的尸体.高度腐烂. 我们正在接近切洛内特.
Texts.Eng: Another zee-beast corpse afloat. So much carrion. We approach the Chelonate.

Texts.Chs: 北方海域.这是雪吗? 当你碰到它的时候,它化为无形的气体.你的船员集中在烟囱附近取暖.
Texts.Eng: Boreal Reach. Is this snow? Touch it, and it puffs to vapour. Your crew huddles close to the warmth of pipe and funnel.

Texts.Chs: 去甲板寻找带火花的锋利金属. 臭氧和电光萦绕在船的四周. 这里就是黎明边缘.
Texts.Eng: Came on deck to find the metal sharp with sparks. Ozonal coronas haunt the ship. This is Dawn's Edge.

Texts.Chs: 令人毛骨悚然的菌丝, 海草,不可名状的植物.我们进入了罗网.
Texts.Eng: Creeping tendrils of fungus, zee-weed, unnamable flora. We enter the Snares.

Texts.Chs: 发现了死亡租界附近的极光蟹幼体.
Texts.Eng: Discovered a group of Auroral Megalops outside the Tomb Colonies.

Texts.Chs: 发现卡米安运河的极光蟹幼体.
Texts.Eng: Discovered the Auroral Megalops of the Cumaean Canal.

Texts.Chs: 发现了来自寒霜城的活冰山!
发现来自苍白之地的活冰山!
Texts.Eng: Discovered the Lifebergs of the Pale Haunt!

Texts.Chs: 发现了许诺之海的孤独锚爪海胆!
Texts.Eng: Discovered the Lorn Flukes of the Promised Sea!

Texts.Chs: 发现了汗国的三体大战舰.
Texts.Eng: Discovered the Trimarans of the Khanate.

Texts.Chs: 发现了来自碎鸦灯塔的暴君蛾.
Texts.Eng: Discovered the Tyrant Moths of The Ragged Crow.

Texts.Chs: 发现来自钢铁共和国的未完成者革命分子.
Texts.Eng: Discovered the Unfinished Revolutionaries of the Iron Republic.

Texts.Chs: 发现了死亡租界附近的蝙蝠群.
Texts.Eng: Discovered the flocks of bats outside the Tomb Colonies.

Texts.Chs: 尘埃, 回声: 就连空气也被黑暗浸染了. 这是死亡租界附近的水域.
Texts.Eng: Dust, echoes: even a sepia tint to the air. These are the waters around the Tomb-Colonies.

Texts.Chs: 遭遇海盗之林的护卫舰!
Texts.Eng: Encountered the pirate fleets of the Corsair's Forest!

Texts.Chs: 离下面一英寻,离上面一英里.
发现了伊伦特海流的铁笼鲨!
Texts.Eng: Found the Bound-Sharks of Errant's Gyrus!

Texts.Chs: 寒霜城, 宏伟而寒冷. 一座被谜语,问题和答案围攻的要塞.
Texts.Eng: Frostfound, vast and chilly. A fortress sieged by questions, answers, and riddles.

Texts.Chs: 在这里,一片黑暗的大海就像泛起波纹的玻璃,夹杂着一点洞顶的微光.
Texts.Eng: Here the slate-black sea is like rippled glass, spiked with light from the roof.

Texts.Chs: 在这里,狂野的空气和其他区域的空气混合在一起. 德莫之门,以在其中失踪的一名领航员命名. 他的遗骨是怎么来到下面的?
Texts.Eng: Here the wilder airs mingle with the airs of the near reaches. Demeaux's Gate, named for a navigator lost above. How did his bones come below?

Texts.Chs: 家乡的水域. 水手们趴在栏杆上,寻找伦敦的灯火.
Texts.Eng: Home waters. Zailors dawdle at the rail, watching for the lights of London.

Texts.Chs: 鋼鐵和米斯里合作公司.真菌林場
小船在附近的海域聚集着. 船员都带着怀念的神情: 他们互相讲述着光明之海的老故事. 我们接近了卡米安运河,通向地表的路.
Texts.Eng: Little ships throng the waters here. The crew grow wistful: they swap old stories of sunlit sea. We draw near to the Cumaean Canal, the way to the Surface.

Texts.Chs: 贩帽人蝙蝠栖息在漏斗状的地形中,用偷来的羽毛装饰自己.这里一定是羽毛海.
Texts.Eng: Milliner-bats perch on the funnel, gaudy with stolen plumage. This must be the Feathered Sea.

Texts.Chs: 新水手不会注意到变化. 但是你感觉空气刺痛了你的皮肤. 某个地方有一些新的变化.
Texts.Eng: No landlubber would notice the change. But you feel the air prickle on your skin. Somewhere new.

Texts.Chs: 帕默斯顿海域. 风中有硫磺的气味.
Texts.Eng: Palmerston's Reach. There is brimstone on the wind.

Texts.Chs: 在船舱的角落里窜来窜去,叽叽喳喳.弓着背的小身影在甲板的围栏上移动着. 拉特西的空气为这些有害动物壮了胆.
Texts.Eng: Scuttering and chittering in the corners of the hold. Humped shapes on the deck rail. Rattsey air emboldens vermin.

Texts.Chs: 牧羊人湾流, 满是咸味的伦敦贫穷离岛, 隐士,修女和秘密交易的家乡.
Texts.Eng: Shepherd's Wash, the salty hinterland of London, home to hermits, nuns and shadowy business.

Texts.Chs: 炽热的蒸汽从海中升腾而出. 时间退居一旁.你看到一名锅炉工的脖子上套上了绳圈,然后他的同伴把它殴打致死.我们正在钢铁共和国的烟幕之下.
Texts.Eng: Sizzling vapours rise from the sea. Time slips sideways. A coil of rope has stung a stoker, and his fellows beat it to death. We are under the hand of the Iron Republic.

Texts.Chs: 有些被遗忘的东西还在这里.
螺塔直指伪星之光.小心礁石.
Texts.Eng: Spined towers rear in the light of the false-stars. Ware reefs.

Texts.Chs: 远处若隐若现的石笋就像是伍夫斯托克港的起重机,但是远比那更巨大,更巨大. 这里就是海盗之林.我们的瞭望手提高了警惕.
Texts.Eng: Stalagmites loom in the distance like the cranes of Wolfstack Docks, but vaster, vaster. The Corsair's Forest. Our lookouts are watchful.

Texts.Chs: 从寒冰后方吹出了奇怪的暖流. 这里是石柱海, 伊瑞暮将会矗立的地方.谎言. 总是在这里游荡.
Texts.Eng: Strange puffs of warmth from the air behind the ice. This is the Pillared Sea, where Irem will lie. Lies. Has always lain.

Texts.Chs: 玛瑙港.遥远南方的小镇,洞顶在光明之山上反射着微光.
Texts.Eng: The Carnelian Coast. Far to the South, the Neath-roof glimmers above the Mountain of Light.

Texts.Chs: 哭泣高地, 蓝色先知呼唤死者之名的地方.
Texts.Eng: The Crying Heights, where the Blue Prophets call the names of those about to die.

Texts.Chs: 珊瑚之源. 这些死去的彩虹在波浪下散发着微光,就像是在回应着上面的伪星.
Texts.Eng: The Principles of Coral. The corpse-rainbow glow from beneath the waves echoes the false-stars above.

Texts.Chs: 许诺之海. 总是这里, 关于溺亡者们谎言的歌声随着风飘荡着.
Texts.Eng: The Promised Sea. All through this place, the song of the Drownies lies shivering-sweet along the wind.

Texts.Chs: 盐阶.这里是新汗国的领土,在伦敦陷落之前,他们的祖先就早已来到这里...
Texts.Eng: The Salt Steppes. This is the domain of the New Khanate, whose ancestors came here long before London fell...

Texts.Chs: 上方的伪星看起来就像阴郁的玛瑙,就像老虎的眼睛.斯坦福的阔地, 以那个孩子被大猫叼走的可怜人命名.
Texts.Eng: The false-stars above are feral amber, like tigers' eyes. Stamford's Expanse, named for one who lost his child to cats.

Texts.Chs: 秋日之海的迷雾会迷住你的眼睛,渗入你的心.你经常发现你会莫名其妙的开始流泪.
Texts.Eng: The mists of the Sea of Autumn get into the eyes, the heart. It is not unusual to find yourself in unsuspected tears.

Texts.Chs: 水流因为其中漂浮的菌丝而变得迟钝. 紫色的蔬菜破土而出. 米瑟利加亚!
Texts.Eng: The water is sluggish with hyphal threads. Violet vegetable bulks break the surface. Myceligaea!

Texts.Chs: 风带来了遥远圣歌的回响. 早已死去的牧师仍然在为这里计时.
Texts.Eng: The wind carries the echo of distant chants. Long-dead priests still count the hours in this place.

Texts.Chs: 世界被看不见的丝线网住了. 你穿过了其中的一个.绷紧了它们, 这些绷紧的丝线能切开水果.
Texts.Eng: The world is webbed with invisible lines. You've crossed one. Tighten them, and it would split like a fruit.

Texts.Chs: 这里的海水有些温暖. 气泡浮起, 爆裂, 似乎是某种懒散的威胁. 地火永不安宁.
Texts.Eng: The zee here is warm. Bubbles rise and burst with lazy menace. The fire in the earth is restless.

Texts.Chs: 这里一定是虚空之隅.空气中有一些辐射发出的寒冷爆裂声. 向北方看去, 伪星陷入了黑暗之中.
Texts.Eng: This must be Void's Approach. The air crackles with frosty radiations. To the North, the false-stars fail in the darkness.

Texts.Chs: 一朵淡黄色的光组成的花朵出现在了南方的地平线上! 你靠近了瓦尔查斯, 镜之城.
Texts.Eng: This part of the Unterzee (The Southern Wall) has not yet been created!

Texts.Chs: 我们接近了手掌帝国.让我们抓紧自己的灵魂, 小心别让圣灵猿从我们身上把灵魂抓走.
Texts.Eng: We approach the Empire of Hands. Let us clasp our souls tight, lest the Pentecost Apes take them from us.

Texts.Chs: 我们进入了风暴之骨.圣艾利吉乌斯让他的火焰在空中起舞, 在甲板上起舞. 我们能看见,在很远的地方,是碎鸦灯塔的光.
Texts.Eng: We enter Stormbones. St Eligius sends his fire to dance in the air, on deck. Very far away we see the great light of the Ragged Crow.

Texts.Chs: 我们驶入了雕像海.巨人们盯着我们.噬王者的城堡就在前面, 那些傻瓜们放弃他们的未来的地方.
Texts.Eng: We have entered the Sea of Statues. Giants gape at us. Kingeater's Castle rises ahead, where fools give up their future.

Texts.Chs: 我们回避着莲花海里面的真菌垫叶. 那里有一座监狱, 被瘤节先知守护着...
Texts.Eng: We watch for fungal-pads in the Sea of Lilies. There is a prison here, guarded by knot-oracles...

Texts.Chs: 沃爾夫岡大帝號的殘骸

Texts.Eng: You have encountered the  Glorious Frigates.

Texts.Chs: 遭遇海盗之林的护卫舰!
Texts.Eng: You have encountered the Iron Republic Dreadnaughts.

Texts.Chs: 你遭遇了在卡米安运河附近捕食的弗拉尔水母.
Texts.Eng: You have encountered the Jillyfleurs that prey on Cumaean shipping.

Texts.Chs: 发现流浪之山, 一座黑色的玻璃山，吞噬船只.
Texts.Eng: discovered Mt Nomad, the black glass mountain that eats ships.
